
Registration
    -Register id                (PK)(auto-increament)
    -first name                 (NOT NULL)
    -middle name
    -last name                  (NOT NULL)
    -mobile no.                 (NOT NULL)  (UNIQUE)
    -email id                   (NOT NULL)  (UNIQUE)
    -password                   (NOT NULL)  (UNIQUE)
    -extra columns

Customer/owner detail / Create profile

    -user id                    (PK)
    -Driving license            (NOT NULL)  (UNIQUE)
    -first name                 (NOT NULL)
    -middle name    
    -last name                  (NOT NULL)
    -contact                    (NOT NULL)  (UNIQUE)
    -email                      (NOT NULL)  (UNIQUE)
    -customer address           (NOT NULL)
    -Aadhar no.                 (NOT NULL)  (UNIQUE)
    -Pan no.                    (NOT NULL)  (UNIQUE)
    -DOB    
    -Gender
    -car id(null if it is a customer)   (FK)
    -extra columns
    
Car detail
    -car id                     (PK)
    -model name                 (NOT NULL)
    -purchase year              (NOT NULL)
    -availibility               (NOT NULL)
    -location id                (FK)    (NOT NULL)
    -no. of seats               (NOT NULL)
    -luggage capacity   
    -cost per hour              (NOT NULL)
    -late fee per hour
    -fuel type                  (NOT NULL)
    -kms drove                  (NOT NULL)
    -transmission               (NOT NULL)
    -mileage                    (NOT NULL)
    -car color  
    -user id                    (FK)    (NOT NULL)
    -insurance                  (BOOLEAN)
    -description                (NOT NULL)
    -extra columns


User location
    -user location id           (PK)
    -street                     (NOT NULL)
    -landmark   
    -city                       (NOT NULL)
    -state                      (NOT NULL)
    -zip code                   (NOT NULL)
    -extra columns
    
Booking details
    -booking id(pk)
    -from DD:HH (date, hour)    (NOT null)
    -to DD:HH (date, hour)      (NOT null)
    -amount per hour            (NOT NULL)
    -status(booked/available)   (BOOLEAN)
    -discount (calculate)       
    -deposit ?                  (NOT NULL)
    -pickup/drop location (user location id)(FK)    (NOT NULL)
    -car id(fk)                 (NOT NULL)
    -customer id(fk)            (NOT NULL)
    -extra columns

Billing details
    -bill id  (PK)   
    -booking id                 (FK)
    -bill date                  (NOT NULL)
    -bill status(paid/pending)  (BOOLEAN)
    -discount amount            
    -total late fees
    -total amount               (NOT NULL)
    -deposit ?                  (NOT NULL)
    -user_id                    (FK)    (NOT NULL)
    -car_id                     (FK)    (NOT NULL)
    -extra columns




